23
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:52,020
[Episode 8]

24
00:01:55,540 --> 00:01:56,340
Do you think

25
00:01:56,420 --> 00:01:58,340
he'll sit over here later?

26
00:01:59,620 --> 00:02:00,260
Waiter.

27
00:02:03,060 --> 00:02:03,540
Of course, he will.

28
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:03,980
Come on.

29
00:02:06,820 --> 00:02:08,300
Come and have some tea.

30
00:02:21,820 --> 00:02:22,380
Thank you.

31
00:02:34,220 --> 00:02:34,940
You didn't

32
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:36,740
even look at me or talk to me

33
00:02:37,060 --> 00:02:38,340
the whole way.

34
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:40,060
Why?

35
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:46,260
If one day,

36
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:47,980
you really enter the Academy,

37
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:50,500
you'll have to call me Senior Brother.

38
00:02:51,460 --> 00:02:52,940
I will take care

39
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:54,700
of your studies and your behavior.

40
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:56,020
By then,

41
00:02:56,420 --> 00:02:58,100
you can't just ignore me

42
00:02:58,180 --> 00:02:59,860
like you do now.

43
00:03:00,580 --> 00:03:02,300
It's not that I ignore you.

44
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:04,220
I'm just a little worried.

45
00:03:04,580 --> 00:03:05,580
I'm worried that you'll think

46
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:06,420
I'm still holding a grudge
against you.

47
00:03:06,620 --> 00:03:07,540
So...

48
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:10,460
I felt a little awkward.

49
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:15,100
He's childish.

50
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:16,220
No.

51
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:18,380
It's called youthfulness.

52
00:03:19,380 --> 00:03:21,780
Okay, tell me

53
00:03:21,820 --> 00:03:23,740
why you think

54
00:03:23,740 --> 00:03:25,100
I would think you hold a grudge
against me.

55
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:26,020
Because you showed up

56
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:27,180
and then my master died.

57
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:29,380
That's a fact.

58
00:03:29,740 --> 00:03:31,100
But those are two different things.

59
00:03:31,420 --> 00:03:32,420
These two things seem

60
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:33,660
to be related,

61
00:03:34,260 --> 00:03:35,460
but in the end,

62
00:03:35,860 --> 00:03:36,660
if I hadn't been

63
00:03:36,660 --> 00:03:37,820
playing sword in Swords Forest,

64
00:03:38,220 --> 00:03:39,260
people wouldn't have thought

65
00:03:39,260 --> 00:03:40,460
that my master was still alive

66
00:03:40,540 --> 00:03:41,780
and hiding in Qiandong City.

67
00:03:42,340 --> 00:03:43,940
Then my master wouldn't be dead.

68
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:47,460
So it appears

69
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:49,380
that the one
who caused my master's death

70
00:03:51,260 --> 00:03:52,020
was me.

71
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:54,100
You mustn't think that way.

72
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:55,100
If you do, you've...

73
00:03:55,380 --> 00:03:56,940
You've got yourself in a bind.

74
00:03:58,780 --> 00:03:59,740
Don't worry.

75
00:04:00,100 --> 00:04:01,580
If I really kept thinking that way,

76
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:02,340
I wouldn't

77
00:04:02,340 --> 00:04:03,460
have been able
to step out of Qiandong City.

78
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:05,780
The real killers of my master

79
00:04:06,060 --> 00:04:07,820
were the two of the unknown,

80
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:09,820
Wufa and Wutian.

81
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:10,740
I'm very clear

82
00:04:10,820 --> 00:04:11,820
about that.

83
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,140
Hence, Mengsha

84
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:14,260
and Little Master,

85
00:04:14,740 --> 00:04:15,660
don't worry about me.

86
00:04:16,140 --> 00:04:17,940
Look.

87
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:18,940
He's so sensible.

88
00:04:19,340 --> 00:04:19,900
He deserves

89
00:04:19,900 --> 00:04:21,340
to be my junior brother in the future.

90
00:04:22,060 --> 00:04:22,860
You're not

91
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:24,540
finished yet.

92
00:04:24,580 --> 00:04:25,100
Yes.

93
00:04:27,900 --> 00:04:29,260
Even though I thought long

94
00:04:29,860 --> 00:04:31,060
about it

95
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:31,940
and tried to convince myself,

96
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:32,740
I still had

97
00:04:32,740 --> 00:04:34,220
a grudge in my heart.

98
00:04:35,100 --> 00:04:36,180
If you hadn't come,

99
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:37,500
maybe my grandfather

100
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:38,420
and my uncle

101
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:39,820
could have protected my master.

102
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:40,740
That's why

103
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:42,900
I still feel like

104
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:45,580
beating you up.

105
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:51,700
All right.

106
00:04:51,980 --> 00:04:53,540
Then wait until the day

107
00:04:53,740 --> 00:04:56,300
you can beat me.

108
00:04:57,860 --> 00:04:59,740
Okay, deal.

109
00:05:01,780 --> 00:05:02,780
Deal.

110
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:03,820
Deal.

111
00:05:10,220 --> 00:05:12,100
You're so arrogant.

112
00:05:12,460 --> 00:05:14,060
Do you know that Xiao Ruofeng

113
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:15,660
is Mr. Li's

114
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:17,140
best disciple?

115
00:05:21,380 --> 00:05:22,100
As for me,

116
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:24,140
I got in a few years before him,

117
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:25,700
but I'm no match for him.

118
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:28,100
I guess you'll have to wait

119
00:05:28,220 --> 00:05:28,860
until you're

120
00:05:28,860 --> 00:05:30,380
in your seventies or eighties
before you can beat him.

121
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,700
Soon, he won't be the best disciple

122
00:05:32,740 --> 00:05:34,260
of Mr. Li.

123
00:05:35,420 --> 00:05:36,100
Why?

124
00:05:36,420 --> 00:05:37,140
Because

125
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:39,300
I'll replace him.

126
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:42,540
Come on.

127
00:05:59,060 --> 00:05:59,820
Young Master.

128
00:06:00,980 --> 00:06:01,740
Young Master.

129
00:06:01,820 --> 00:06:02,460
What happened?

130
00:06:02,460 --> 00:06:03,900
The letter from the Academy has arrived.

131
00:06:04,020 --> 00:06:05,380
It's for you to be the examiner

132
00:06:05,380 --> 00:06:07,220
for the Academy's
preliminary examination.

133
00:06:07,740 --> 00:06:09,180
The man made it a point to emphasize

134
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:10,660
that this was a notification,

135
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:11,580
not a discussion.

136
00:06:15,340 --> 00:06:16,300
Master knows

137
00:06:16,300 --> 00:06:18,060
I don't like to show my face in public,

138
00:06:18,260 --> 00:06:19,420
but he wants me to be

139
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:20,540
the examiner
for the preliminary examination.

140
00:06:22,140 --> 00:06:23,420
What a playful old man.

141
00:06:25,180 --> 00:06:27,620
It's called being able
to do what others can't,

142
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:29,420
but not what others can.

143
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:31,660
To put it simply,

144
00:06:31,980 --> 00:06:33,340
it's just a way to make fun of us

145
00:06:33,580 --> 00:06:34,460
and to make things difficult for us

146
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:35,660
for fun.

147
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:41,580
Do you think Baili Dongjun

148
00:06:41,580 --> 00:06:42,740
will be disappointed

149
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:44,660
when he enters the Academy

150
00:06:44,900 --> 00:06:46,100
and finds out that he already knows

151
00:06:46,620 --> 00:06:47,780
his future senior brother?

152
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:52,300
Young Master,

153
00:06:52,700 --> 00:06:53,540
I thought

154
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:54,860
that even

155
00:06:54,860 --> 00:06:56,460
the person chosen by Little Master

156
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:57,140
would have

157
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:58,580
to pass the Academy's examination.

158
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:01,060
But why do you make it sound

159
00:07:01,780 --> 00:07:02,580
as if this person

160
00:07:02,580 --> 00:07:04,100
will definitely be Baili Dongjun?

161
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:08,820
This is a good question.

162
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:17,260
Since it's a good question,

163
00:07:17,260 --> 00:07:18,580
just answer me.

164
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:28,460
I guess I'll have to think carefully
about the questions

165
00:07:29,220 --> 00:07:30,540
for the preliminary examination.

166
00:07:36,090 --> 00:07:38,470
[Two weeks later]

167
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:43,870
[Tianqi]

168
00:07:47,340 --> 00:07:48,580
Tianqi City.

169
00:07:50,580 --> 00:07:52,100
We've finally arrived.

170
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:56,700
I've lived in Tianqi before,

171
00:07:57,140 --> 00:07:58,860
but I've never seen the gate properly.

172
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:00,260
I heard
that the White Feather Sword Deity

173
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:01,540
once came to Tianqi

174
00:08:01,940 --> 00:08:02,780
to save his disciple

175
00:08:02,780 --> 00:08:03,820
from being beheaded.

176
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:04,820
Before he left,

177
00:08:05,220 --> 00:08:06,820
he smashed the plaque with his sword.

178
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:09,860
None of the world's masters dared
to stop him.

179
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:12,540
This story is true.

180
00:08:12,660 --> 00:08:13,620
I want to do that, too.

181
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:15,860
No.

182
00:08:16,260 --> 00:08:17,940
It's a capital offense.

183
00:08:17,940 --> 00:08:18,860
Did the White Feather Sword Deity

184
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:19,740
get beheaded?

185
00:08:20,780 --> 00:08:22,300
Who could have had him beheaded?

186
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:24,420
He's the Sword Deity.

187
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:25,180
I'll wait

188
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:26,220
until I've become a deity.

189
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:28,100
I'll then smash this plaque
with my sword.

190
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:31,900
I'll part ways

191
00:08:31,900 --> 00:08:32,500
with you two here.

192
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:33,580
Second Senior,

193
00:08:34,540 --> 00:08:35,820
take Dongjun back to the Academy.

194
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:37,300
I'm going into the palace first.

195
00:08:52,100 --> 00:08:52,660
Let's go.

196
00:09:02,540 --> 00:09:03,540
The roads in Tianqi City

197
00:09:04,060 --> 00:09:05,100
are still as wide as ever.

198
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:07,380
It's much bigger than Qiandong City.

199
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:09,940
It's perfect for a trip.

200
00:09:09,980 --> 00:09:10,980
Indeed.

201
00:09:11,060 --> 00:09:12,060
Back in the day,

202
00:09:12,100 --> 00:09:13,340
Gu Jianmen and I used

203
00:09:13,340 --> 00:09:15,260
to travel side by side in Tianqi City.

204
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:17,820
Now he's tied up in Gu Family's affairs

205
00:09:18,420 --> 00:09:19,580
in Xinan Circuit.

206
00:09:20,260 --> 00:09:20,980
Since you're interested

207
00:09:20,980 --> 00:09:22,220
in exploring this place,

208
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:24,100
I'll return to the Academy first.

209
00:09:34,460 --> 00:09:36,140
Young Lady, Second Young Lady.

210
00:09:44,900 --> 00:09:45,660
Yueyao.

211
00:09:46,300 --> 00:09:48,300
[Yueqing, Sky's Beyond]
There are freshly sliced beef, mutton,

212
00:09:48,340 --> 00:09:49,940
fish slices as thin as a cicada's wing,

213
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:51,660
and mushrooms only produced in Nanjue.

214
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:53,220
What do you think?

215
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:54,380
What's good to eat first?

216
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:55,740
I know

217
00:09:55,740 --> 00:09:56,980
you're the best to me.

218
00:09:57,660 --> 00:09:59,620
Knowing that you miss having hot pot,

219
00:09:59,980 --> 00:10:01,980
Young Lady warmed up the pot
and cooked the meat

220
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:02,740
early in the morning.

221
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:03,500
That's for sure.

222
00:10:03,580 --> 00:10:04,660
She's my sister.

223
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:07,740
Eat slowly.

224
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:09,220
There's a lot of good food.

225
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:10,580
I went to a lot of fun places

226
00:10:10,580 --> 00:10:11,780
this time

227
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:13,860
and brought back a lot of new things.

228
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:15,820
I've got rice cake from Jiangnan

229
00:10:16,100 --> 00:10:17,540
and sausages from Shuofeng.

230
00:10:17,780 --> 00:10:19,420
You can have anything you want.

231
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:22,020
Yueyao, I want to eat them all.

232
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:24,380
Did you guys have any fun

233
00:10:24,500 --> 00:10:25,860
on your trip to Chaisang?

234
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:27,980
I've heard it's a very prosperous place

235
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:29,580
with a lot of good liquor.

236
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:31,500
Yueyao, did you bring some back?

237
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:40,340
Qing, since when did you

238
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:41,940
start enjoying drinking?

239
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:45,100
The trip

240
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:46,300
was so rushed

241
00:10:46,620 --> 00:10:47,740
that I forgot to bring some back.

242
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:50,460
It's okay. You can go again next time.

243
00:10:54,820 --> 00:10:55,500
Young Lady.

244
00:11:02,260 --> 00:11:04,060
Young Lady, Second Young Lady.

245
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:05,340
It's you, Mo Qixuan.

246
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:06,500
Sit down and eat with us.

247
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:16,180
Let's talk outside.

248
00:11:32,260 --> 00:11:32,980
What's the matter?

249
00:11:33,620 --> 00:11:36,380
Baili Dongjun has arrived at Tianqi.

250
00:11:36,740 --> 00:11:37,620
Tianqi?

251
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:41,580
Now, at this time of year,

252
00:11:43,780 --> 00:11:44,620
he is going to...

253
00:11:44,620 --> 00:11:45,460
Yes.

254
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:48,260
To sit the examination of the Academy.

255
00:11:51,780 --> 00:11:52,460
Xin,

256
00:11:53,500 --> 00:11:54,140
what is it

257
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:55,740
that they need to go out and talk about?

258
00:11:56,020 --> 00:11:57,260
Did you encounter any problems

259
00:11:57,460 --> 00:11:58,540
on your trip?

260
00:11:58,860 --> 00:12:00,740
Yueyao seems to have a lot on her mind.

261
00:12:01,660 --> 00:12:02,740
Young Lady...

262
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:03,500
Xin,

263
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:04,380
get me another plate

264
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:05,380
of mutton later.

265
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:06,540
That meat is delicious.

266
00:12:06,740 --> 00:12:08,020
And the mushrooms, too.

267
00:12:08,460 --> 00:12:09,620
I got it.

268
00:12:10,460 --> 00:12:11,740
What did you say about Yueyao?

269
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:13,780
Nothing.

270
00:12:14,100 --> 00:12:15,140
Just enjoy your food.

271
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:16,100
Your sister

272
00:12:16,140 --> 00:12:17,140
is just fine.

273
00:12:25,540 --> 00:12:27,980
Young Lady, there's no time
for hesitation.

274
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:30,260
If he really enters the Academy...

275
00:12:33,780 --> 00:12:35,540
If he really enters the Academy...

276
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:39,740
and has Mr. Li's protection,

277
00:12:40,780 --> 00:12:41,900
Beique...

278
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:47,260
won't have a chance anymore.

279
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:52,500
Miss Fairy,

280
00:12:52,900 --> 00:12:53,860
are you leaving?

281
00:12:54,860 --> 00:12:56,140
You haven't told me your name.

282
00:12:56,620 --> 00:12:57,860
How am I going to find you?

283
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:10,380
♪Wind blows through the window lattice♪

284
00:13:11,580 --> 00:13:13,780
♪It's raining in martial world♪

285
00:13:14,820 --> 00:13:19,280
♪And the stars are flitting
in the mist-covered waters♪

286
00:13:21,460 --> 00:13:23,900
♪How many people in the world♪

287
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:26,840
