00:25:11,980 --> 00:25:12,860
Unless...

582
00:25:15,260 --> 00:25:16,700
he's really a good-for-nothing!

583
00:25:19,140 --> 00:25:19,940
Why does Little Master

584
00:25:19,940 --> 00:25:21,140
want a good-for-nothing?

585
00:25:21,140 --> 00:25:22,380
Who knows?

586
00:25:23,540 --> 00:25:24,980
Maybe in a few years,

587
00:25:26,420 --> 00:25:28,100
he won't be a good-for-nothing.

588
00:25:30,780 --> 00:25:31,700
Is it funny?

589
00:25:35,820 --> 00:25:36,740
Where is Tu Wan?

590
00:25:37,460 --> 00:25:38,540
He's gone to listen to the song.

591
00:25:39,260 --> 00:25:40,580
He's a good-for-nothing, too.

592
00:25:41,180 --> 00:25:42,140
He can't do anything.

593
00:25:42,140 --> 00:25:43,500
What he cares about
is just to feed himself.

594
00:25:45,460 --> 00:25:46,700
Get me someone

595
00:25:47,340 --> 00:25:47,940
to find out more

596
00:25:47,940 --> 00:25:49,860
about the man Little Master brought back.

597
00:25:50,060 --> 00:25:50,620
Yes, sir.

598
00:25:50,780 --> 00:25:51,660
Come back.

599
00:25:53,260 --> 00:25:55,260
Go to the treasury and get 1,000 taels

600
00:25:55,940 --> 00:25:56,740
of gold.

601
00:25:57,700 --> 00:25:59,740
Get someone to make a bet for me.

602
00:26:00,740 --> 00:26:01,580
On whom?

603
00:26:04,580 --> 00:26:06,740
On Little Master's Choice.

604
00:26:07,580 --> 00:26:08,220
Yes, sir.

605
00:26:10,100 --> 00:26:10,940
Go on with the massage.

606
00:26:27,060 --> 00:26:27,860
Sir.

607
00:26:29,740 --> 00:26:30,740
As you predicted,

608
00:26:31,020 --> 00:26:32,460
Young Lady's traveled alone to Tianqi.

609
00:26:35,820 --> 00:26:37,620
Young Lady is gentle and indecisive.

610
00:26:37,780 --> 00:26:39,260
She seems to be swayed

611
00:26:39,260 --> 00:26:40,540
by the idea of restoring the country.

612
00:26:40,660 --> 00:26:42,220
Besides, it's hard for her

613
00:26:42,300 --> 00:26:44,620
to bring back Baili Dongjun alone.

614
00:26:47,060 --> 00:26:48,340
You and Qixuan

615
00:26:48,340 --> 00:26:49,860
go there secretly.

616
00:26:50,260 --> 00:26:51,340
If necessary,

617
00:26:51,460 --> 00:26:53,020
you can help her.

618
00:26:54,300 --> 00:26:54,940
Yes.

619
00:26:56,060 --> 00:26:58,340
No news of Wufa and Wutian yet?

620
00:27:00,500 --> 00:27:01,900
Lord Wufa and Lord Wutian

621
00:27:02,060 --> 00:27:03,740
lost half of their powers
to the Scholarly Deity

622
00:27:04,100 --> 00:27:04,780
and ran away

623
00:27:04,780 --> 00:27:05,740
with their meridians broken.

624
00:27:06,140 --> 00:27:07,420
Since then, they've disappeared.

625
00:27:07,940 --> 00:27:09,180
Our men searched for them

626
00:27:09,260 --> 00:27:10,340
but to no avail.

627
00:27:12,900 --> 00:27:13,700
Fine.

628
00:27:14,220 --> 00:27:15,500
This time, I'll ask Wuzuo

629
00:27:15,500 --> 00:27:16,740
to go with you.

630
00:27:17,100 --> 00:27:18,460
He's departed.

631
00:27:19,300 --> 00:27:20,420
He'll help you

632
00:27:20,860 --> 00:27:22,260
if he has to.

633
00:27:23,820 --> 00:27:25,980
We've been away from home too long.

634
00:27:27,700 --> 00:27:28,540
So long

635
00:27:30,060 --> 00:27:31,820
that many of us

636
00:27:33,340 --> 00:27:35,180
have forgotten what home is like.

637
00:27:35,860 --> 00:27:37,660
Only when the Chief finishes his retreat

638
00:27:37,700 --> 00:27:39,380
and we all work together

639
00:27:40,220 --> 00:27:41,780
can we go back.

640
00:27:46,260 --> 00:27:48,780
I'll do whatever it takes

641
00:27:49,060 --> 00:27:50,540
to fulfill my duty.

642
00:27:52,540 --> 00:27:53,380
What did you say?

643
00:27:55,460 --> 00:27:56,940
You're the one I trust the most.

644
00:27:57,740 --> 00:27:59,220
How dare you tell Lord Wuxiang

645
00:27:59,500 --> 00:28:00,820
