646
00:28:02,540 --> 00:28:03,780
I have

647
00:28:04,540 --> 00:28:05,460
no choice but to do so.

648
00:28:05,540 --> 00:28:07,100
What are you

649
00:28:07,180 --> 00:28:08,220
talking about?

650
00:28:09,140 --> 00:28:10,020
Qixuan.

651
00:28:11,420 --> 00:28:12,620
