of your internal strength?

663
00:29:45,380 --> 00:29:46,420
Why do you still think

664
00:29:46,420 --> 00:29:47,500
I'm pretending?

665
00:29:47,780 --> 00:29:50,060
I told you I didn't know how to do it.

666
00:29:50,140 --> 00:29:51,180
I meant it.

667
00:29:53,900 --> 00:29:55,060
That's impossible.

668
00:29:55,180 --> 00:29:56,220
If you don't have any internal strength,

669
00:29:56,300 --> 00:29:56,940
how can you use

670
00:29:56,940 --> 00:29:57,980
the Western Chu's Sword Song?

671
00:30:00,940 --> 00:30:01,700
I got it.

672
00:30:02,500 --> 00:30:03,380
Your master

673
00:30:03,380 --> 00:30:04,580
must have blocked

674
00:30:04,780 --> 00:30:05,500
all your internal strength

675
00:30:05,500 --> 00:30:06,540
by some means.

676
00:30:07,740 --> 00:30:08,500
How about this?

677
00:30:09,180 --> 00:30:09,740
I

678
00:30:09,780 --> 00:30:10,500
will teach you a set

679
00:30:10,500 --> 00:30:11,820
of internal strength techniques
for breathing.

680
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:12,540
Let's see

681
00:30:12,620 --> 00:30:13,980
if it can draw
out your internal strength.

682
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:16,220
You don't need to thank me.

683
00:30:20,340 --> 00:30:21,460
Looks like I have to pack up

684
00:30:21,460 --> 00:30:22,460
and go back to Qiandong City.

685
00:30:23,180 --> 00:30:24,380
How can a disciple
of the Scholarly Deity

686
00:30:24,740 --> 00:30:25,460
give up

687
00:30:25,460 --> 00:30:26,460
so easily?

688
00:30:28,840 --> 00:30:30,940
