695
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:14,300
but have no internal strength,

696
00:31:14,380 --> 00:31:15,260
you're just nothing.

697
00:31:20,500 --> 00:31:21,820
I told you, without internal strength,

698
00:31:22,020 --> 00:31:23,580
how powerful can your fist be?

699
00:31:34,820 --> 00:31:35,500
Stop.

700
00:31:37,060 --> 00:31:38,060
Let's stop fighting.

701
00:31:38,460 --> 00:31:39,660
Don't test me anymore.

702
00:31:39,660 --> 00:31:41,020
That's all I've got.

703
00:31:41,340 --> 00:31:42,460
I'm not hiding anything.

704
00:31:45,500 --> 00:31:46,420
Test?

705
00:31:47,340 --> 00:31:48,420
Who do you think I am?

706
00:31:52,220 --> 00:31:52,860
You?

707
00:31:53,660 --> 00:31:54,860
Aren't you one of those disciples

708
00:31:55,020 --> 00:31:56,220
from the Affiliated Academy?

709
00:31:57,540 --> 00:31:59,020
Lei Mengsha is right.

710
00:31:59,180 --> 00:32:00,780
Tianqi City has many talents.

711
00:32:00,940 --> 00:32:02,340
I've come all this way for nothing.

712
00:32:02,660 --> 00:32:03,620
I'll be laughed at by my father

713
00:32:03,620 --> 00:32:04,580
when I'm back.

714
00:32:06,340 --> 00:32:07,460
I've heard a lot

715
00:32:07,460 --> 00:32:08,140
about you

716
00:32:08,140 --> 00:32:09,140
and I was interested in you.

717
00:32:09,460 --> 00:32:10,740
Yet after a few days,

718
00:32:11,260 --> 00:32:12,940
you've become so dejected.

719
00:32:13,100 --> 00:32:14,180
If you dare humiliate me,

720
00:32:14,220 --> 00:32:14,980
