Who are you?

735
00:32:38,980 --> 00:32:40,180
How did you know all this?

736
00:32:41,020 --> 00:32:42,940
I know a lot more.

737
00:32:43,020 --> 00:32:43,940
I know a lot of things

738
00:32:43,940 --> 00:32:44,980
you don't.

739
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:47,260
The reason why your master did this

740
00:32:47,500 --> 00:32:49,260
was because he was afraid
that someone would find out

741
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:50,140
before it was the right time.

742
00:32:50,420 --> 00:32:51,900
So he put a restraint on you

743
00:32:52,060 --> 00:32:53,380
to block your internal strength.

744
00:32:53,580 --> 00:32:54,380
Unless

745
00:32:54,860 --> 00:32:56,780
you can't control yourself,

746
00:32:57,380 --> 00:32:58,220
like

747
00:32:58,820 --> 00:32:59,580
when you're drunk.

748
00:33:03,340 --> 00:33:04,460
You're a friend of my master's?

749
00:33:05,460 --> 00:33:06,060
But you sound

750
00:33:06,060 --> 00:33:07,380
so young.

751
00:33:08,220 --> 00:33:09,340
Young doesn't mean weak.

752
00:33:09,700 --> 00:33:10,700
Mr. Li of the Academy,

753
00:33:10,700 --> 00:33:11,580
the Sword Deities
and the Scholarly Deity of Western Chu

754
00:33:11,580 --> 00:33:12,420
were only young

755
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:13,540
when they became famous.

756
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:15,660
I'm not really friends
with the Scholarly Deity,

757
00:33:15,860 --> 00:33:17,260
but we had a connection.

758
00:33:17,460 --> 00:33:18,780
I owe him a favor.

759
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:20,180
So now

760
00:33:20,540 --> 00:33:21,540
it's time to return

761
00:33:21,540 --> 00:33:22,380
the favor.

762
00:33:22,980 --> 00:33:25,780
Can you help me with the restraint?

763
00:33:26,180 --> 00:33:27,500
If you try to forcibly
remove the restraint,

764
00:33:27,940 --> 00:33:29,060
years of internal strength

765
00:33:29,060 --> 00:33:30,460
will instantly flood through your body.

766
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:32,500
Either you die or you'll be crippled.

767
00:33:32,860 --> 00:33:33,660
Besides,

768
00:33:34,580 --> 00:33:35,260
I'm not going

769
00:33:35,260 --> 00:33:36,460
to do it the hard way.

770
00:33:38,780 --> 00:33:40,580
My way is the only

771
00:33:40,820 --> 00:33:42,300
and best way.

772
00:33:42,780 --> 00:33:43,540
What's it?

773
00:33:44,300 --> 00:33:46,140
Let your internal strength slowly

774
00:33:46,220 --> 00:33:48,500
integrate into your body
little by little.

775
00:33:49,300 --> 00:33:50,060
How?

776
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:51,220
Learn internal strength techniques.

777
00:33:55,940 --> 00:33:56,740
In the end, your style

778
00:33:56,740 --> 00:33:57,860
is the same as Lei Mengsha's.

779
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:58,580
Forget it.

780
00:33:58,900 --> 00:34:00,260
It's just a few days away.

781
00:34:00,380 --> 00:34:00,780
If we can train

782
00:34:00,780 --> 00:34:01,940
our internal strength in a few days,

783
00:34:01,980 --> 00:34:03,740
then there will be many great masters
in the world.

784
00:34:03,820 --> 00:34:04,860
Do you think I'm stupid?

785
00:34:05,100 --> 00:34:06,260
But you're not like them.

786
00:34:06,700 --> 00:34:07,580
The internal strength techniques
I'm talking about

787
00:34:07,580 --> 00:34:09,020
aren't the same as Lei Mengsha's.

788
00:34:12,660 --> 00:34:13,660
I'll come again tonight.

789
00:34:15,940 --> 00:34:16,940
I'm not free tonight.

790
00:34:17,260 --> 00:34:19,020
The weak have no right to say no.

791
00:34:19,420 --> 00:34:20,020
You...

