00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:27,320
[Mount Wangcheng]

793
00:34:48,540 --> 00:34:49,260
Yunyang.

794
00:34:50,220 --> 00:34:52,500
Martial Uncle Wang, you're back.

795
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:01,940
After finishing this one,

796
00:35:02,540 --> 00:35:04,260
