00:35:05,070 --> 00:35:08,620
[Zhao Yuzhen, Disciple of Lyu Suzhen,
Mount Wangcheng]

798
00:35:09,780 --> 00:35:11,300
One more,

799
00:35:12,340 --> 00:35:14,740
and I'll have to wait till next year.

800
00:35:19,020 --> 00:35:19,660
Yuzhen.

801
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:26,180
Yixing.

802
00:35:27,100 --> 00:35:28,020
Yuzhen.

803
00:35:30,260 --> 00:35:32,260
Yuzhen, you haven't
finished the peaches yet.

804
00:35:32,540 --> 00:35:33,300
Yes.

805
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:36,020
But only the last two are left.

806
00:35:36,460 --> 00:35:37,220
Yixing,

807
00:35:37,700 --> 00:35:39,220
why do you think

808
00:35:39,260 --> 00:35:42,180
peaches only grow in summer and fall?

809
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:44,340
Why don't we have peaches

810
00:35:44,340 --> 00:35:45,740
all year round?

811
00:35:46,060 --> 00:35:47,260
It's only when everything
lies dormant in winter

812
00:35:47,460 --> 00:35:48,820
that the flowers bloom in spring

813
00:35:49,020 --> 00:35:50,340
and the summer and fall
are brought to fruition.

814
00:35:50,820 --> 00:35:52,500
There's a rule for everything.

815
00:35:52,580 --> 00:35:53,700
Just go with the flow.

816
00:35:57,100 --> 00:35:59,060
But I want to eat peaches every day.

817
00:35:59,220 --> 00:36:00,380
Everything has a rule,

818
00:36:00,540 --> 00:36:01,700
so I'll change it

819
00:36:01,700 --> 00:36:02,980
and make it serve a better cause.

820
00:36:05,620 --> 00:36:07,660
Yixing, is it fun outside the mountain?

821
00:36:08,700 --> 00:36:09,380
Not bad.

822
00:36:09,700 --> 00:36:11,780
Good liquor and beautiful ladies

823
00:36:12,060 --> 00:36:13,220
