824
00:36:14,260 --> 00:36:16,020
I'd like to go down the mountain too.

825
00:36:19,860 --> 00:36:20,420
Look

826
00:36:20,700 --> 00:36:21,860
what I've brought you.

827
00:36:22,140 --> 00:36:22,820
A sword?

828
00:36:25,540 --> 00:36:26,740
This is no ordinary sword.

829
00:36:27,020 --> 00:36:27,780
This is the sword

830
00:36:27,820 --> 00:36:28,940
made from the Xuanyang Sword's blank

831
00:36:29,460 --> 00:36:30,860
