832
00:36:31,100 --> 00:36:32,340
It's the warmest sword on earth.

833
00:36:32,820 --> 00:36:34,660
If you bury this sword in the ground,

834
00:36:35,020 --> 00:36:37,380
it'll keep the whole yard in spring.

835
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:38,340
You

836
00:36:38,460 --> 00:36:39,900
have got to get better
at practicing Fire Arts.

837
00:36:40,020 --> 00:36:40,620
By then,

838
00:36:40,700 --> 00:36:41,980
it won't be a problem for you

839
00:36:42,060 --> 00:36:43,100
to crave peaches in the winter.

840
00:36:45,260 --> 00:36:47,460
