841
00:36:47,580 --> 00:36:48,260
The God of Fire.

842
00:36:48,740 --> 00:36:49,900
What an awful name.

843
00:37:16,180 --> 00:37:16,940
Split.

844
00:37:22,460 --> 00:37:23,260
Combined.

845
00:37:29,220 --> 00:37:30,940
You can use it this way?

846
00:37:30,980 --> 00:37:32,260
You can use it this way?

847
00:37:32,580 --> 00:37:33,420
Yes.

848
00:37:33,740 --> 00:37:35,660
That's the way it works.

849
00:37:37,060 --> 00:37:37,900
Yixing.

850
00:37:38,860 --> 00:37:39,940
You're back.

851
00:37:42,170 --> 00:37:44,340
[Lyu Suzhen, Chief of Mount Wangcheng]

852
00:37:45,140 --> 00:37:46,060
- Master.
- Chief.

853
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:48,180
I'll leave you all to it.

854
00:37:48,540 --> 00:37:49,420
I'm off now.

855
00:37:54,740 --> 00:37:55,540
Take it.

856
00:38:07,580 --> 00:38:08,380
Master,

857
00:38:08,660 --> 00:38:09,540
Yuzhen was talking

858
00:38:09,540 --> 00:38:10,460
about going down the mountain again.

859
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:12,500
I read Yu's fortune

860
00:38:12,940 --> 00:38:14,500
when he was born.

861
00:38:14,660 --> 00:38:17,540
Whether it's secret techniques
or swordsmanship,

862
00:38:18,060 --> 00:38:18,900
he'll be

863
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:20,900
the best at Mount Wangcheng
